 You can have all these other things, and without the core, you know,

00:36:21.000 --> 00:36:25.000
 it really doesn't work. It really can go really wrong.

00:36:25.000 --> 00:36:29.000
 Or it can just not really, you know, the result is we fizzle out, you know,

00:36:29.000 --> 00:36:32.000
 and we blame the Dharma, and we blame all these things, you know.

00:36:32.000 --> 00:36:35.000
 Without that basic core, you know.

00:36:35.000 --> 00:36:39.000
 That's the great secret of the Dharma, of the Mahayana.

00:36:39.000 --> 00:36:42.000
 The secret the Revachay say at the beginning, every time.

00:36:42.000 --> 00:36:46.000
 Cultivate compassion. Everyone's like, "Oh, I want the secret teachings!"

